    "text": [
        "alssalamu `alayka ya mawlaya",
        "ya aba muhammadin alhasanu bna `aliyyin",
        "alhadi almuhtadi",
        "wa rahmatu allahi wa barakatuhu",
        "alssalamu `alayka ya waliyya allahi wabna awliya'ihi",
        "alssalamu `alayka ya hujjata allahi wabna hujajihi",
